    Author

    ExtractionPlugin

    ImmutableTrace

    LatLong

    MaturityLevel

    PluginId

    PluginInfo

    A builder for plugin information.
    PluginResources

    PluginResources.Builder
    Builder for PluginResources.
    PluginType
    The type of plugin, which describes its function.
    RandomAccessData

    SearchResult

    SearchTrace

    Trace
